<h1><FONT COLOR= "#012169"> About Lion Tutor </FONT COLOR= "#012169"></h1>
<br></br>
<h5> <FONT COLOR= "808080"> We are committed solving one of the most common pain points that every student faces here at Columbia, which is finding a TA to help them with topics they are struggling with in their courses.</h5>
<h5> According to our research, there is around 1 TA for every 80 students. <h5>
<h5> We propose combatting this problem by introducing Lion Tutor <h5>
<h5> We will be connecting struggling students with fellow classmates who are experts on specific topics and would like to help their fellow peers by sharing their knowledge.</h5>
<h5> As a reward, these Lion Tutors can receive extra credit from their Professors. </h5>
